### Step 3 — Update & Answer

#### Update State

```
up   = new_up   = [0, 2, 3]
down = new_down = [3, 2, 0]
```

#### All Length-3 Sequences in DP

```
up   (ending with UP move):
  index 0, value 1: 0 sequences
  index 1, value 2: 2 sequences
  index 2, value 3: 3 sequences

down (ending with DOWN move):
  index 0, value 1: 3 sequences
  index 1, value 2: 2 sequences
