## Key Formulas Summary

```
┌──────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Formula          │ Meaning                                            │
├──────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ up[v] = i        │ base: i values smaller than v exist                │
│ down[v] = m-1-i  │ base: m-1-i values larger than v exist             │
│ pref_up[i]       │ sum of up[0..i]                                    │
│ pref_down[i]     │ sum of down[0..i]                                  │
│ new_up[v]        │ = pref_down[v-1]  (previous DOWN, now go UP)       │
│ new_down[v]      │ = total_up - pref_up[v]  (prev UP, now go DOWN)    │
│ answer           │ = sum(up) + sum(down)  after n-1 transitions       │
└──────────────────┴────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

